OL,3,CWhat is Cardiff Crossrail and when
OL,4,Cwill it be built?
OL,6,FNew images have been released of the
OL,7,Ffirst phase of the proposed Cardiff
OL,8,FCrossrail project.
OL,10,FThe initial stage would see the
OL,11,Fconstruction of a tramway linking
OL,12,FCardiff Central railway station and
OL,13,FCardiff Bay.
OL,15,FCardiff Council and Transport for
OL,16,FWales say the scheme will complement
OL,17,Fthe ongoing South Wales Metro work to
OL,18,Fincrease the frequency and speed of
OL,19,Fservice on the existing Cardiff Bay
OL,20,Fline.
