OL,3,CWhat is Cardiff Crossrail and when
OL,4,Cwill it be built?
OL,6,FA six-week public consultation begins
OL,7,Fon Monday.
OL,9,FThe scheme is eventually intended to
OL,10,Frun from the north west of the capital
OL,11,Fto Splott and Newport Road in the
OL,12,Feast, eventually joining up with the
OL,13,Fproposed Cardiff Parkway station at St
OL,14,FMellons.
OL,16,FThese further phases, however, would
OL,17,Frequire many hundreds of millions of
OL,18,Fpounds in extra funding.
