OL,3,CWhat is Cardiff Crossrail and when
OL,4,Cwill it be built?
OL,6,FFinal approval of the privately funded
OL,7,FCardiff Parkway is in the hands of the
OL,8,FWelsh Government, who called in the
OL,9,Fplans and held further hearings at the
OL,10,Fstart of the year.
OL,12,FCardiff Council unveiled its initial
OL,13,Fconcept for Cardiff Crossrail in
OL,14,FJanuary 2020.
OL,16,FThis first phase is jointly funded by
OL,17,F#50m secured by Cardiff Council from
OL,18,Fthe UK Government's Levelling Up fund,
OL,19,Fand #50m from the Welsh Government.
