OL,3,CWhat is Cardiff Crossrail and when
OL,4,Cwill it be built?
OL,6,FCardiff Council and Transport for
OL,7,FWales say the route could be up and
OL,8,Frunning by early 2029, with work
OL,9,Fbeginning once the project is
OL,10,Fofficially signed off by the UK
OL,11,FGovernment.
OL,13,FBut the scheme will not currently
OL,14,Fextend to the proposed station at
OL,15,FPierhead Street to directly serve the
OL,16,Fnew 15,000 capacity arena due to be
OL,17,Fbuilt in Cardiff Bay.
