OL,3,CWhat is Cardiff Crossrail and when
OL,4,Cwill it be built?
OL,6,FA consultation over the route of the
OL,7,Ffuture eastern spur, running through
OL,8,FCardiff Bay to Splott and onwards to
OL,9,FNewport Road, was held in 2023.
OL,11,FHow does Cardiff Crossrail fit in with
OL,12,Fthe South Wales Metro?
OL,14,FConsiderable work is continuing to
OL,15,Felectrify what Transport for Wales
OL,16,Fcalls the 'Core Valley Lines', the
OL,17,Frail routes from Cardiff to
OL,18,FTreherbert, Merthyr Tydfil, Aberdare
OL,19,Fand Rhymney, along with other branches
OL,20,Fto Coryton and via Radyr.
