OL,3,CWhat is Cardiff Crossrail and when
OL,4,Cwill it be built?
OL,6,FThe promise is for faster and more
OL,7,Ffrequent services from 2025.
OL,9,FNew trains are already running on some
OL,10,Froutes, but the 'tram train' vehicles
OL,11,Fthat will form the backbone of the
OL,12,Fservice are not due to take passengers
OL,13,Funtil next year.
OL,15,FThese trains can run to a lighter
OL,16,Fstandard than traditional heavy rail,
OL,17,Fmeaning they can run on the kind of
OL,18,Froutes being proposed for Cardiff
OL,19,FCrossrail.
