OL,3,CWhat is Cardiff Crossrail and when
OL,4,Cwill it be built?
OL,6,FWith the Welsh Government having
OL,7,Fambitious targets to encourage more
OL,8,Fpeople to use public transport,
OL,9,Foffering attractive alternatives to
OL,10,Fcar use is key.
OL,12,FBut the project has been hit by delays
OL,13,Fand rising costs, with Transport for
OL,14,FWales citing Covid and the cost of
OL,15,Fmaterials.
OL,17,FThe project has already seen many
OL,18,Fmiles of track electrified and doubled
OL,19,Fup, with new platforms along the
OL,20,Froutes.
