OL,3,CWhat is Cardiff Crossrail and when
OL,4,Cwill it be built?
OL,6,FCardiff Crossrail is intended as an
OL,7,Fambitious addition to the network,
OL,8,Fconnecting parts of the capital and
OL,9,Fwider region not currently served by
OL,10,Frail.
OL,12,FBut with public finances already
OL,13,Fstretched, funding the future
OL,14,Fextensions to this route may be
OL,15,Fchallenging.
